@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pavzjn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.52)) / wp.sin((v0 + 0.63 + tmp + 0.42)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.43) / (v2 + 0.86 - v0 + 0.80)))
    v0 = (0.58 / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.23) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.11)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.94 + tmp + 0.46)) - tmp)
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
